posts.subject: Behold - the webm that killed a nation.
I'm not insane. YOU are insane.
posts.body:
When I see this - I see highwaymen. Or a shadow government squeezing taxes from poor peasants.

Not only do I intend to thwart you - I become obsessed about killing every onel of you. Making sure that none escape. Actually am mentally calculating the time it would take to kill every one of you while you are busy scattering.

Am I perfect? Not at all. So it's wrong to put the public in danger when this fight is really just between us.

So as compensation for the karma risk you commit me to, along with the certainty of my own demise at the hands of LE - I firmly intend to kill all your relatives. Every one I can get my hands on. Thanks to the wallets and ID I pull from your dead bodies. A promise.

So just don't do this. The entire country awaits an explosion of vengeance upon you. If they can delay my death - they will.

You are now on many minds. This awareness will never stop. The public has many scores to settle with you. You and your offspring are marked forever.

Yes, I will enjoy killing you. You are bullies. Who doesn't enjoy killing bullies?
